          "body": {
            "text": "Landsort, or Öja as the island is actually called, lies south of Nynäshamn. It is reached by ferry from Ankarudden. There is a bus to Ankarudden. Alternatively, you can get there by your own boat. There is a guest harbour in Skravleviken near the northern tip of the island.",
